previous.excerpt:
I met Tommy in real life and took him shopping! It was very awesome.

gents: @TommyInnit @JackManifoldTV 
- edited by @LlamaNeck 

Follow my Twitter - @TubboLive

Follow my Instagram - @TubboLive

Today I met TommyInnit (creator of the Minecraft But and also You Laugh You Lose challenge), & Jack Manifold in real life! It was so funny and we had lots of laughs and fun and pog. This is a vlog like other vloggers but I am the best vlogger. We had funny moments and even talked about the Dream SMP and our War VS Dream in Minecraft. It was so fun and Pog Champ
previous.title: I Took Tommy Shopping...

localize.title: I Took Tommy Shopping...
localize.description:
リアルにTommyに会って、買い物に連れて行ってもらいました とても素晴らしかったです。

紳士の皆様。トミー・インニット @ジャック・マニホールドTV 
- 編集者: @LlamaNeck 

ツイッターをフォローする - @TubboLive

私のインスタグラムをフォローする - @TubboLive

今日はTommyInnit（Minecraft Butの作者であり、You Laugh You Loseチャレンジの作者でもある）と、Jack Manifoldにリアルに会ったよ。とても面白くて、たくさん笑って楽しんで、ポグをしました。これは他のブロガーと同じVlogですが、私は最高のブロガーです。私たちは面白い瞬間を過ごし、ドリームSMPやMinecraftでの私たちの戦争VSドリームについても話しました。とても楽しかったですし、Pog Champ

localize.title: 我带着汤米去购物...
localize.description:
我在现实生活中见到了汤米，并带他去购物！这让我感到非常高兴。那是非常棒的。

先生们。@TommyInnit @JackManifoldTV 
- 编辑：@LlamaNeck 

关注我的Twitter - @TubboLive

关注我的Instagram - @TubboLive

今天我遇到了TommyInnit（Minecraft的创造者，但也是You Laugh You Lose的挑战），和Jack Manifold在现实生活中！它是如此的有趣，我们有很多的机会。这是非常有趣的，我们有很多的笑声和乐趣和pog。这是一个像其他vlogger的vlog，但我是最好的vlogger。我们有有趣的时刻，甚至谈到了梦想SMP和我们的战争VS梦想在Minecraft. 它是如此的有趣和Pog冠军

localize.title: 我帶着湯米去購物...
localize.description:
我在現實生活中見到了湯米，並帶他去購物！這讓我感到非常高興。那是非常棒的。

先生們。@TommyInnit @JackManifoldTV 
- 編輯：@LlamaNeck 

關注我的Twitter - @TubboLive

關注我的Instagram - @TubboLive

今天我遇到了TommyInnit（Minecraft的創造者，但也是You Laugh You Lose的挑戰），和Jack Manifold在現實生活中！它是如此的有趣，我們有很多的機會。這是非常有趣的，我們有很多的笑聲和樂趣和pog。這是一個像其他vlogger的vlog，但我是最好的vlogger。我們有有趣的時刻，甚至談到了夢想SMP和我們的戰爭VS夢想在Minecraft. 它是如此的有趣和Pog冠軍

next.excerpt:
Could it be?? Dollightful’s first ever ball jointed doll is here! Simple and cute, this little bunny BJD was designed by yours truly and brought to life with the help of my wonderful husband! 

Here are the free STL files!
https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:4845451

Mentioned in video:
Dive.hara “Bisque Dolls” Maker: http://divehara.com/category/bisque-doll/53/
Instagram: dive.h
--------------------------------------------
Merchandise:
https://www.zazzle.com/store/dollightful/collections
https://society6.com/dollightful
Doll clothing patterns here: https://www.etsy.com/shop/DollightfulPatterns
Instagram, Twitter, Pinterest: @dollightfully
--------------------------------------------
MATERIALS
Home-made Bunny ball jointed doll! See above link for STL files.
Sculpting kit from https://www.etsy.com/shop/TheDollPlanetHair
Elastic – 1mm
Fabric – cotton
Ribbon – 3/8 inch/9.5 mm 
Paints – Acrylic (Liquitex)
Paints – Gouache (Caran D’ache)
Water Color Pencils (Faber Castell)
Varnish (DuraClear)
Resin – 2-Part Jewel Resin (www.clayndeco.com)
Gram Scale
Resin Eye Molds (Padico) I used the 10mm size hemisphere.
Paint for eye whites – Game Air “Dead White” (Vallejo)
Glue (205 OKONG 오공본드)
--------------------------------------------
Musical tracks from:
Dylan the Druid: https://soundcloud.com/dylan-mccoy-638351878
--------------------------------------------
Musical tracks from:
Artlist https://artlist.io 
Squeaky Clean by Josh Leake
Grind and Skip by Bamtone 
Cheerful by Bamtone
Brand New Toy by Ty Simon 
Baby Smile by Lux Inspira
--------------------------------------------
Logo and other graphics designed by: https://charliesparksdesign.myportfolio.com/
--------------------------------------------
